ldpreload_patcher
=================

Patch a binary on load time:
============================

1. Figure out what and where to patch
2. Use patch(address_to_patch, patch_to_apply, length_of_patch, mprotect_permissions), to do the patching. 
3. ???
4. PROFIT!

Hijack a function(x86 only for the moment):
==========================================

1. Figure out where the function is located
2. Use hijack_function(address_of_old_function, address_of_new_function)
3. ???
4. PROFIT!
